01:23:22.364 --> 01:23:25.265
Nah, I'm just a character
in a novel.

01:23:25.267 --> 01:23:27.801
Yeah, but you
wrote that novel.

01:23:27.803 --> 01:23:29.470
Well buddy, now
it's your turn.

01:23:30.639 --> 01:23:31.972
What are you gonna do?

01:23:33.075 --> 01:23:37.611
I'm gonna live
forever, man.

